Use the standard library
This is how to is_happy of s:
   Remember that n is s's length
   When n is less than 2, then:
      The answer is 0
   End when
   Remember that i is 1
   Do this diff of n and 1 times:
      When item i in s is at most item (diff of i and 1) in s, then:
         The answer is 0
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is 1
Now you know